{"tid":1357226,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵職員：不合作運動有咩用","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T17:46:36.000Z","uid":275109,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf30ca4293a82b1b49fffdde3be84b7976d9356c","tid":1357226,"uid":275109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:26:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有用！每一件事都有佢嘅價值！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要達到每一個成功，都必然會經歷艱辛和喜悅：<br />\n但請緊記鬥奮過後才是勝利。</span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJUSkA5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJUSkA5.png&h=02acf134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想當年甘地發起世界歷史上第一個全國性的<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">非暴力</span></span>反抗運動，又稱非暴力不合作運動。<br />\n甘地呼籲以非暴力的不合作手段（例如：不納稅、不入公立學校、不入公職，並多次絕食），抵制英國的統治。<br />\n運動使當地的殖民政府近乎<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓</span></span>，迫使英國政府不得不頒布新憲法，讓印度逐漸發展自治體制。<br />\n<br />\nSource: Wikipedia"},{"pid":"24dc57b73adb91917877a76878013abf0398f35f","tid":1357226,"uid":275109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:31:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7:30 一齊金鐘塔鐵</span>"},{"pid":"9ce66c76805d6e0a6f12479056dd5f396ba14129","tid":1357226,"uid":129309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24dc57b73adb91917877a76878013abf0398f35f","tid":1357226,"uid":275109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:31:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7:30 一齊金鐘塔鐵</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:44:28.000Z","msg":"係真既要預早做定文宣"},{"pid":"9c09dd1b8332aaff65dcd319692304d2db18d061","tid":1357226,"uid":73621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:46:36.000Z","msg":"抵d狗鐵職員日日都比我撚到狗咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各行各業入黎曬 staff card <br />\n<br />\n[附